ren


ren *.file-extension ???-file-name.*
rename all the files with the specific extension by leaving the first three characters of the old names and appending other content to the name.

ren *.* ?????.*
rename files by trimming the old names longer than five characters.

ren old-file-name-part*.* new-filename-part*.*
rename files by replace a part of the old names with a new part.

ren "GoodBay.txt" "////*.txt"
GoodBay.txt -> Bay.txt

